raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do Story.mabel_kissed(\"Player\")
Mabel: Babe? You still on the bus home?
Player: Yep!
Mabel: Okay good 😊
Mabel: So... 👀
Mabel: That happened huh? 🫠
Player: You okay? 😆
Mabel: I'm FINE
Mabel: Totally fine
Mabel: Thought: Head totally not blanking again
Mabel: Thought: Just had my first kiss, no big deal!!
Player: I wish we were still on the park bench hehe
Mabel: That was supposed to be my top secret relaxation spot
Mabel: I guess I can make an exception for you
Mabel: Since you took me there at night... it was a whole different mood 😊
Player: It was nice just sitting there with you
Mabel: \"Just sitting\" yeah right!! 🙃
Player: Okay maybe not JUST sitting 😆
Mabel: Thought: It was perfect though
Mabel: Was I any good at it? Y'know..
Player: You mean kissing?
- I enjoyed it 🥰
	Player: I enjoyed it 🥰
	Mabel: Me too 🥰
- You were great
	Player: You were great
	Mabel: Really??
	Mabel: That makes me feel all giddy hehe
- Someone's gonna get lucky at the party
	Player: Someone's gonna get lucky at the party
	Mabel: Omg... 🥹
	Mabel: That's like the weirdest compliment ever babe
	Mabel: Thought: Being that intimate with someone else is... I don't know
	Player: It's true! 😆
Mabel: Do you have the pictures? ☺️
Player: Mhmm!
Mabel: Show me already silly 😚
Mabel: Can't wait to see all the faces we made hehe
Player: img: mabel/160
Mabel: Omg why do I look so little even when I'm on your lap!!
Player: You're my short queen!
Mabel: Don't you dare call me that!
Player: Short? I thought you didn't mind that lol
Mabel: I'm not a queen, I'm a princess 🥰
Player: Seriously, THAT was your worry? 😂
Mabel: 😂
Mabel: Is that silly or what?
Mabel: I'd smooch you again right now if I could 😚
Player: 😚
Mabel: Was there another picture?
Player: You bet
Player: img: mabel/161
Mabel: Thought: Why do I look so aggressive!!
Mabel: Thought: Bad angle right?? Must be..
Mabel: Oh my god 😩
Mabel: Seriously, who thinks to just lay in the grass like that
Player: And who thinks to follow my lead 😏
Player: Besides, it was nice and cool grass!
Mabel: It was SO PRICKLY and cold babe omg
Mabel: PinkThought: But you were all soft and warm
Mabel: The stars were really pretty though ☺️
- I was looking at you more
	Player: I was looking at you more
	do heart(2)
	Mabel: 🥴
	Mabel: You can't just SAY stuff like that
	Mabel: PinkThought: My heart is doing backflips right now
- Super beautiful
	Player: Super beautiful
	Mabel: It really was ☺️
	Mabel: Thought: I wonder if he noticed me staring at him instead
Player: Pretty sure your eyes were all hungry for me 😂
Player: Are you sure you even looked at the stars?
Mabel: Did too!
Mabel: PinkThought: Besides.. can you blame me for focusing on you?
do heart(0)
Mabel: Kissing under the stars though 😶
Mabel: That sounds so cheesy but it wasn't too bad
Player: Not bad!? 😂
Mabel: !!
Mabel: I didn't mean it that way omg
Mabel: Just that I always imagined it to be somewhere bright and sunny
Mabel: I loved it though, I swear 🥹
Mabel: Thought: I hope he doesn't think I'm unsatisfied. It really was
Player: I know, just teasing
Mabel: Meanie 👊👊
Mabel: Actually I wanted to ask you for something 😶
Player: What's with that expression? 😆
Mabel: Remember when I uhm.. wanted to see you without your shirt on? 🙈
do heart(1)
Player: How could I forget 😉
Mabel: Well... I just wanted to have a picture of that on my phone..
- Of course!
	Player: Of course!
	Mabel: Yay 🥳
	Mabel: Thought: Thank god he's not teasing me about this
- How badly do you want it?
	Player: How badly do you want it?
	Mabel: 🙈
	Mabel: Badly, pretty pleaaase
Player: Here it is haha
Player: img: mabel/156
Mabel: 😍😍😍
Mabel: PinkThought: Goosebumpss!!!
Player: You really wanted it off 😄
Mabel: I'm just a girl with girl thoughts gee 😇
- Have you been looking at other guys? 😏
	Player: Have you been looking at other guys? 😏
	Mabel: THAT'S A SECRET!!
	Mabel: Thought: Okay maybe one... or two? no, three guys on social
	Mabel: Thought: But only because I'm curious!!
- Did you like what you see?
	Player: Did you like what you see?
	Mabel: I did 🫣
	Mabel: 👉👈
	Mabel: It was perfect 🥰
Mabel: My hands were literally shaking did you notice?? 😭
Player: I did, was cute as heck!
Mabel: CUTE?? I didn't come off as a nervous wreck again? 😣
Mabel: PinkThought: I wonder what would have happened if we didn't stop...
do heart(1)
Mabel: Anyway!!
Mabel: At least now the party won't be so scary 😅
Player: Since you got some practice in? 😏
Mabel: DON'T call it practice 😭
Mabel: It was special okay!?
Player: I know, I'm kidding 😊
do heart(1)
Mabel: But really though
Mabel: I had a really good time last night ☺️
Mabel: Like a REALLY good time 🥰
- Me too ❤️
	Player: Me too ❤️
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: 🥰
- We should do that again sometime
	Player: We should do that again sometime
	do heart(2)
	Mabel: The park or the... other part? 👀
	Player: Both 😏
	Mabel: PinkThought: Yes please
	Mabel: I mean... if you want to 😇
Player: Bus is pulling over!
Mabel: Okay! Get home safe 😊
Mabel: Love you!! 😘
Player: Love you too! 😍
=> END
"
